Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{=32}===============================DIALOGUE============================
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.99,0:02:21.75,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,O tempo está ótimo!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.42,0:02:29.25,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,A Grand Line\Né pra bem longe daquele lado?!{OG}{Is the Grand Line far,\Nfar away in that direction?! - arch}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.55,0:02:32.72,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Ou será que é pra cá?!{Or is it maybe this way?! - OG}{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.09,0:02:34.84,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Pra lá?! Pra cá?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.97,0:02:37.68,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Isso é muito empolgante!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.68,0:02:39.68,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Você é irritante.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.68,0:02:41.14,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Fica quieto, vai!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.14,0:02:43.14,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Desculpa! Desculpa!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.14,0:02:48.90,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Agora que finalmente temos um cozinheiro,\Nsó falta trazer a Nami de volta!{But we finally have a cook,\Nso now we just need to get Nami back - OG}{Now that we finally have a cook,\Nwe just need to get Nami back. - Gaijin}{AR}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.90,0:02:51.11,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Aí finalmente vamos\Npra Grand Line!{and then we're finally going\Ninto the Grand Line! - OG}{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.73,0:02:53.49,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Nami, né?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.49,0:02:57.74,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Só de lembrar do belo rosto dela\Njá me sinto animado.{Just remembering her beautiful\Nvisage makes me happy! - OG}{Just remembering her beautiful\Nfigure makes me happy! - arch}{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.28,0:03:00.33,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Mal posso esperar pra vê-la de novo!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.37,0:03:03.83,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Ei, Yosaku.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.83,0:03:06.29,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Estamos quase chegando onde a Nami está, né?{OG}{We're almost at the place where Nami is, right? - arch}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.58,0:03:10.55,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Pessoal, fiquem sérios! Isso não é brincadeira!{You guys're soft-minded!\NToo soft-minded! - OG}{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.55,0:03:11.75,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Vocês não entendem?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.75,0:03:16.84,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Estamos indo direto pro\Ncovil do famigerado Arlong!{\fad(0,936)}{Minute by minute, we're heading\Nright for the infamous Arlong! - OG}{Gaijin}{Minute by minute, we're heading right towards Arlong's place! - arch}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.60,0:03:22.39,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Quando a Mana viu\No cartaz de procurado do Arlong...{Big Sis' eyes were glued to\NArlong's picture when she saw it! - OG}{At that moment, Big Sis' eyes were glued to Arlong's picture! - arch}{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.39,0:03:24.85,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,ela não conseguiu tirar os olhos dele!{Big Sis' eyes were glued to\NArlong's picture when she saw it! - OG}{At that moment, Big Sis' eyes were glued to Arlong's picture! - arch}{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.89,0:03:28.86,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Ela ficou parecendo outra pessoa!{She wasn't her normal self! - OG}{Her whole demeanor changed! - WF}{WF+Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.03,0:03:39.70,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,A Mana Nami deve estar atrás da\Nrecompensa de vinte milhões de berries do Arlong!{Big Sis Nami plans to take down Arlong and collect his 20-million-belly bounty! - OG}{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.70,0:03:43.54,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Ela já pode estar\Ndentro do território dele agora!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.54,0:03:46.96,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Bom, vamos comer alguma coisa.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.96,0:03:47.54,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,É.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.83,0:03:53.67,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Não me digam que vocês\Nnunca ouviram falar do Arlong?!{Don't tell me you guys've\Nnever heard of Arlong?! - OG}{PP}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.67,0:03:54.84,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Arlong?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.84,0:03:55.59,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Sei lá.{Never heard of him. - OG}{No clue. - WF}{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.18,0:04:03.01,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Tá bom, prestem atenção!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.01,0:04:05.85,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Acho que vou ter que explicar tudo pra vocês!{I guess I'll just have to fill\Nyou in about everything! - OG}{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.68,0:04:11.19,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Arlong é um homem-peixe que causou\Nestragos por toda a Grand Line!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.19,0:04:12.19,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Homem-peixe?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.19,0:04:14.82,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Um homem-peixe, é? Nunca conheci um.{A fishman, huh?\NI haven't met one yet. - OG}{arch: OG is too literal imo}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.82,0:04:17.65,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Sabe, em algum lugar\Nda Grand Line, dizem que existe{Say, I hear the mermaids on Fishman Island in the Grand Line - OG}{Say, I hear that\NFishman Island in the Grand Line is - arch: reword for CPS}{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.65,0:04:20.78,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,um lugar chamado Ilha dos Homens-Peixe\Ncheio de sereias lindas!{are absolutely beautiful! - OG}{full of beautiful mermaids! - arch}{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.16,0:04:22.41,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Os homens-peixe se parecem...{Are fishmen... - OG}{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.28,0:04:24.04,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,com isso?{THAT LAUGH LMAO, WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.58,0:04:26.79,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Que obra-prima!{\an8}{That's a masterpiece! - OG}{AR}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.95,0:04:28.25,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Vocês não conseguem se concentrar?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.96,0:04:32.00,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Tá bom. Vou começar do início.{Alright then. I'll explain from the very beginning. - OG}{CPS, WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.75,0:04:37.01,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Primeiro, o motivo da Grand Line\Nser chamada de Cemitério de Piratas{The reason the Grand Line's called\Na pirate graveyard in the first place - OG}{Do you know why the Grand Line\Nis called the Pirate Graveyard? - WF}{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.01,0:04:39.47,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,é por causa de três grandes poderes\Nque governam aquele lugar.{is because of the three\Npowers that reign over it. - OG}{is because of the three\Ngreat powers that reign over it. - Gaijin}{Well, there are three\Ngreat powers governing it. - WF}{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.88,0:04:43.85,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Um deles são os\NSete Guerreiros do Mar!{OG}{And one of them is\Nthe Seven Warlords of the Sea! - WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.43,0:04:48.23,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Sete Guerreiros?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.77,0:04:51.69,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Resumindo, eles são\Nos piratas do próprio governo.{Simply put, they're\Ngovernment-authorized pirates. - OG}{Simply put, they're privateers. - Gaijin}{Basically, they're privateers. - WF}{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.69,0:04:53.27,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Tá de brincadeira?{What? - OG}{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.27,0:04:57.11,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Por que piratas teriam\Naprovação do governo?{\fad(0,980)}{Why would pirates\Nget a government's approval? - OG}{Why would pirates get\Nthe government's approval? - Gaijin}{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.74,0:05:02.74,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Eles podem agir livremente porque\No governo recebe uma parte{By paying the government a cut\Nof the loot they take from pirates, - OG}{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.74,0:05:04.91,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,do que eles saqueiam\Nde outros piratas.{the Seven Warlords\Nare allowed to exist! - OG}{the Seven Warlords\Nare allowed to roam free! - arch: OG's is too literal}{CPS, also feel it answers Sanji's question better moved around like this, WF+GD}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.66,0:05:09.66,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Pra outros piratas, eles não passam\Nde cães do governo,{In other pirates' eyes, they're\Nno more than "government dogs," - OG}{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.66,0:05:11.25,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,mas são incrivelmente fortes!{but they're strong! - OG}{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.96,0:05:22.59,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Entre eles está o homem\Nque derrotou o Zoro, Olhos de Falcão Mihawk!{Even Hawk Eye Mihawk, the guy\NBig Bro Zoro lost to, is a Warlord! - OG}{\q2}{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.59,0:05:24.39,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Isso é insano!{That's awesome! - OG}{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.39,0:05:26.85,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{There's seven of those guys?! - OG}Existem sete caras como {\i1}ele{\i0}?!{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.85,0:05:28.60,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Os Sete Guerreiros são demais!{The Seven Warlords are awesome! - OG}{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.60,0:05:34.56,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Bom, um dos Sete Guerreiros\Né o Jinbe, chefe dos Piratas Homens-Peixe.{So, one of the Seven Warlords is\NJinbe, a fishman pirate boss. - OG}{So, one of the Seven Warlords is\NJinbe, the Fishman Pirates' boss. - Gaijin}{So, one of these Seven Warlords is\NJinbe, the Fishman Pirates' boss. - arch}{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.23,0:05:38.11,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Ele e o Arlong lutavam\Nlado a lado como iguais,{And the fishman Arlong is\Na pirate right on par with him - OG}{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.11,0:05:42.57,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,cometendo atrocidade atrás de\Natrocidade na Grand Line.{who used to commit atrocity\Nafter atrocity in the Grand Line! - OG}{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.78,0:05:45.83,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Assim?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.83,0:05:48.79,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Isso é só o seu último\Ndesenho de pé!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.45,0:05:54.92,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Arlong subjugou vinte cidades\Ndesde que chegou no East Blue!{Arlong has rule over 20 towns\Nsince coming to the East Blue! - OG}{Arlong has taken over twenty towns\Nsince coming to the East Blue! - Gaijin}{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.92,0:05:58.75,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Ele faz o Don Krieg parecer fichinha!{His strength is\Nfar superior to Don Krieg's! - OG}{He's far stronger than Don Krieg! - Gaijin}{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.13,0:06:03.59,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Mas por que a Nami iria\Natrás desse cara sozinha?{But why would Nami-san go\Nto this guy all by herself? - OG}{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.34,0:06:07.22,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Eu falei, ela deve querer\Na recompensa pela cabeça dele!{I told you, she's after\Nthe bounty on his head! - OG}{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.22,0:06:08.31,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Não sei...{No, who knows? - OG}{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.31,0:06:11.35,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Talvez a Nami seja uma sereia!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.35,0:06:14.19,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Ela com certeza é linda o suficiente!{Especially given how lovely she is! - OG}{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.98,0:06:15.77,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Assim?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.77,0:06:18.19,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Eu te mato, seu desgraçado!{I'll kill you! - OG}{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.57,0:06:22.07,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Vocês entenderam alguma coisa\Ndo que eu acabei de dizer?!{Do you guys even understand\Nwhat I've told you?! - OG}{GD}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.07,0:06:25.16,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Sim, tem um homem-peixe forte,\Nné? A gente entendeu!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.66,0:06:28.12,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Não, vocês não entenderam!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.12,0:06:30.12,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Vocês não sabem\No quão fortes são os homens-peixe!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.54,0:06:32.58,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,A gente descobre quando chegar lá.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.58,0:06:34.08,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Para de se preocupar.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.58,0:06:37.04,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Enfim, vamos comer alguma coisa.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.50,0:06:39.05,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,É! Comida!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.67,0:06:40.88,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Opa? Comida?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.34,0:06:42.72,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,O que vocês querem?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.72,0:06:44.97,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Eu quero carne no osso!{Meat things with bones in it! - OG}{Meat things with bones in them! - arch}{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.97,0:06:46.76,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Eu quero moyashi refogado!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.76,0:06:47.72,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Beleza!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.72,0:06:48.68,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Deixa comigo!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.31,0:06:51.43,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Fica pronto num instante!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.02,0:06:53.31,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Carne e moyashi...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.10,0:06:57.40,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Ter um cozinheiro é o melhor!{Having a cook really is great! - OG}{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.40,0:06:58.27,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,É-É!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.65,0:07:00.27,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Carne! Um monte de carne!{Meat! A jumbo serving of meat! - OG}{Meat! A huge serving of meat! - Gaijin}{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.27,0:07:02.78,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,E moyashi pra mim!\NUma porção enorme!{And bean sprouts for me!\NA jumbo serving! - OG}{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.50,0:07:17.54,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Certo.{All right. - OG}{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.54,0:07:20.29,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Aqui está o pagamento deste mês. Aceite.{Here is this month's amount. Accept it. - OG}{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.30,0:07:22.80,Main-207-,,0,0,10,,Meu caro Arlong.{Arlong-kun. - OG}{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.80,0:07:24.88,Main-207-,,0,0,10,,Você tem uma abordagem diferente{You're on a completely different level - OG}{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.88,0:07:26.88,Main-207-,,0,0,10,,dos piratas comuns.{of intellect than ordinary pirates. - OG}{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.88,0:07:28.76,Main-207-,,0,0,10,,Você sabe como o mundo funciona.{You truly know how to\Nget ahead in the world. - OG}{CPS, WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.85,0:07:33.47,Main-207-,,0,0,10,,Igualmente!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.47,0:07:37.73,Main-207-,,0,0,10,,Ser meu amigo significa que você pode\Nexplorar o East Blue à vontade!{Befriending me means you can\Nmilk the East Blue all you want! - OG}{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.35,0:07:42.69,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Esse é um pensamento bem esperto\Npra um capitão da Marinha.{For a Marine captain,\Nyou're wise to realize that! - OG}{You're pretty smart\Nfor a Marine captain. - WF}{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.07,0:07:44.32,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Muito obrigado, como sempre.{Thanks, as always. - OG}{PP's TL - basically, it's a polite thanks to say to someone who has helped you a lot/multiple times. Literally translated it's like "sorry for all the trouble"}{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.32,0:07:47.91,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Por que a formalidade de repente?{Now you say that? - OG}{Why so stuffy/stodgy? - WF}{Quit being so stuffy. - feel like a phrasing more like this flows into the next line smoother, WF}{PP's TL - this is like "why are you being so polite/formal NOW? (after all the times we've worked together)"}{Z/PJ}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.91,0:07:50.66,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,O dinheiro faz o mundo girar.{A good world is one\Nin which money flows well! - OG}{The world is better off\Nwhen cash flows easily. - Gaijin}{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.41,0:07:52.37,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Dinheiro é rei.{Money is good. - OG}{Money is great. - Gaijin}{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.37,0:07:54.62,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Você pode confiar nele mais do que em qualquer coisa.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.04,0:07:56.58,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Não concorda?{Wouldn't you agree? - OG}{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.33,0:07:58.71,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,De fato...{I-Indeed... - OG}{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.71,0:08:03.67,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Eu odeio humanos, mas pessoas\Nrazoáveis como você são exceção.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.38,0:08:05.84,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Bem...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.84,0:08:06.97,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Preciso ir.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.47,0:08:09.93,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Qual a pressa?\NFica e toma uma bebida.{Come drink with us sometime!\NLet's have fun! - OG}{Come drink with us\Nsometime! It'd be fun! - Gaijin}{WF}{PP's TL - i think this translation is very literal, but it's meant to be an invitation to drink now, instead of in the future. like this meaning-wise "you don't have to always go right away, c'mon, drink with us from time to time"}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.80,0:08:15.89,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Navios de patrulha da Marinha não devem\Nser vistos atracados na ilha de um pirata.{It's not good for a Marine ship on patrol\Nto be stopped at a pirate island. - OG}{A naval patrol ship shouldn't\Ndock at a pirate's island. - Gaijin}{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.89,0:08:19.85,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Eu mato qualquer um que te\Ndenunciar pro quartel-general.{I'll kill anyone for you\Nwho tells headquarters. - OG}{I'll kill anyone who tells\Nheadquarters for you. - Gaijin}{WF+Lorphex}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.85,0:08:21.69,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Não precisa. Já estou de saída.{No, I'll be leaving. - OG}{Well, I'll be leaving. - Gaijin}{Perhaps some other time. - WF}{PP's TL - this is him politely declining while bidding farewell}{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.11,0:08:24.19,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Ei, o capitão está indo embora!{Hey! The captain's heading back! - OG}{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.19,0:08:26.32,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Escoltem ele até o navio!{Take him to his ship! - OG}{Lorphex}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.32,0:08:27.86,Main-207-,,0,0,10,,Entendido!{Right! - OG}{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.45,0:08:31.87,Main-207-,,0,0,10,,Entra no pote de polvo! Eu te levo!{Get in the octopus pot! I'll take you there! - OG}{\q2}{CPS, WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.87,0:08:34.45,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Certo. Obrigado.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.45,0:08:37.83,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Mas sabe, eu não supero\No quão engraçada sua cara é.{But you always have such a funny face! - OG}{You always have such a funny face! - Gaijin}{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.83,0:08:40.00,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Parece igualzinha a de um rato!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.96,0:08:42.67,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Ei! Hachi!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.67,0:08:43.96,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Cuidado com o que fala!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.96,0:08:45.80,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,O capitão é nosso convidado de honra!{The captain is a valued guest! - OG}{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.80,0:08:48.34,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Ah, é mesmo! Desculpa!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.34,0:08:50.34,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Não se preocupe, tudo bem.{No, it's alright. - OG}{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.26,0:08:55.97,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Tá bom! Lá vamos nós!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.72,0:08:58.23,Thoughts-207-,,0,0,0,,Malditos homens-peixe...{You damn fishmen. - OG}{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.23,0:09:00.31,Thoughts-207-,,0,0,0,,Eles me dão arrepios.{You're creepy as hell. - OG}{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.31,0:09:02.44,Thoughts-207-,,0,0,0,,Mas o dinheiro deles é bom!{But you're great as pay dirt! - OG}{But your money's good! - Gaijin}{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.45,0:09:19.54,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Ei, você! Sai da frente!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.58,0:09:23.04,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Eu vim matar o Arlong!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.04,0:09:26.00,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Arlong matou meu papai!{He killed my father. Prepare to die. - WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.51,0:09:31.05,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Sai da frente, ou eu mato você também!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.68,0:09:32.55,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Ei!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.51,0:09:40.81,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Arlong não tem tempo\Npra lidar com pirralhos como você!{Arlong doesn't have time to\Nbother with little brats like you! - OG}{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.65,0:09:44.61,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Entendeu? Agora vai pra casa!{Now go home! - OG}{PP+WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.61,0:09:49.99,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Pega isso e cuida de você.{Use that to at least keep yourself safe. - OG}{Just take this and look after yourself. - Gaijin}{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.90,0:09:52.70,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Droga!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.58,0:10:02.62,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Ah! Você voltou, Nami!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.62,0:10:04.29,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Você ficou fora um tempão!{That was a long trip! - OG}{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.29,0:10:06.54,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,E aí? Como foi a colheita dessa vez?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.54,0:10:08.67,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Consegui uma grana enorme!{Couldn't have gone better!\NI earned a ton! - OG}{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.67,0:10:11.34,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{I found so many suckers who are fooled so easily! - OG}{I found so many suckers\Nwho were fooled so easily! - arch: It's still terrible but at least the grammar sounds right}There were plenty of suckers to scam{WF}!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.34,0:10:12.51,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Olha só!{As you can see! - OG}{Look here! - arch: It's still terrible but at least the grammar sounds right}{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.26,0:10:16.47,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Traição realmente é o seu forte!{Betrayal is your forte! - OG}{PP+WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.01,0:10:18.18,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Você me bajula.{I guess. - OG}{If you say so. - WF}{WF}{PP's TL - somewhat humble agreement to arlong's line, it could be anything that fits the character and scene}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.81,0:10:20.35,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Ei! Irmãos!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.35,0:10:23.14,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Nossa camarada\Nvoltou! Vamos festejar!{Our friend has returned! Prepare a party! - OG}{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.23,0:10:25.10,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,É a Nami!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.10,0:10:28.15,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,A Nami voltou!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.25,0:10:52.76,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,F-F-Finalmente chegamos!\NAquilo é o Arlong Park!{W-W-We're finally here! Arlong Park! - OG}{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.22,0:10:59.85,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Então esse é o esconderijo do Arlong,\No homem-peixe da Grand Line?!{So this is the hideout of the fishman Arlong, who came from the Grand Line?! - OG}{Gaijin}{So this is the hideout of Arlong,\Na fishman from the Grand Line...?! - WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.52,0:11:04.27,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Será que a Nami está mesmo aqui?{Is Nami really here?! - OG}{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.06,0:11:08.86,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,A Mana Nami estava no {\i1}Going Merry{\i0},
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.86,0:11:12.23,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,então vamos primeiro verificar\Nse ele está atracado nesta ilha!{so let's first see if it's\Nstopped on this island or not! - OG}{so let's first see if it's\Ndocked on this island! - Gaijin}{so let's first see if it's\Ndocked at this island or not! - arch}{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.23,0:11:13.53,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,B-Boa ideia!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.12,0:11:20.45,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Vamos invadir.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.79,0:11:24.91,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,P-Por que vamos\Nfazer isso de repente?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.33,0:11:28.79,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Você é idiota?! A gente nem\Nencontrou nenhuma pista ainda!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.21,0:11:31.25,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Estamos lidando com homens-peixe, sabia?!{We're dealing with\Nthose fishmen, you know! - OG}{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.25,0:11:33.26,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Precisamos de um plano!{We gotta have a strategy first! - OG}{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.26,0:11:35.34,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Não tem tempo pra isso.{Forget that tedious stuff. - OG}{We don't have time for that. - Gaijin}{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.80,0:11:39.35,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,O Luffy mandou a gente trazer ela de volta.{Luffy told me to bring her back. - OG}{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.35,0:11:41.76,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,E é isso que vamos fazer, não importa\Ncom quem estejamos lidando!{I'm gonna do just that,\Nno matter who we're dealing with! - OG}{So that's what I'm gonna do,\Nfishmen be damned! - WF}{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.39,0:11:43.60,Thoughts-207-,,0,0,0,,– Isso é ruim.\N– Isso é ruim.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.93,0:11:44.98,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Vamos!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.19,0:11:53.57,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Ali está! Achei!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.94,0:11:56.53,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{It's the Going Merry! It's over there! - OG}É o {\i1}Going Merry{\i0}!\NPor que ele está ali?{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.95,0:12:00.37,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Então a Mana Nami {\i1}está{\i0} aqui!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.37,0:12:04.45,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Ei, seus desgraçados!\NQual é a ideia?! Me desamarrem!{Hey, you! What's the big idea?! Untie me! - OG}{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.87,0:12:09.04,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Estamos bem a leste do Arlong Park...\Nna Vila Cocoyashi.{We're farther east of Arlong Park...\NCocoyashi Village. - OG}{We're farther east of Arlong Park...\Nat Cocoyashi Village. - Gaijin}{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.04,0:12:10.29,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Mas é estranho.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.29,0:12:13.63,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Por que o navio está atracado\Ntão longe da vila?{Why's the ship stopped\Nso far from the village? - OG}{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.63,0:12:15.46,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Eu disse pra me desamarrar!{Untie me! - OG}{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.84,0:12:19.47,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Você quase morreu por causa do ferimento!{You've been hurt so bad\Nyou're nearly dead! - OG}{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.47,0:12:21.14,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Fica quieto aí!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.47,0:12:26.10,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Deixa esse comigo!{Just leave this all to me! - OG}{Leave this all to me! - Gaijin}{PP}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.31,0:12:31.69,Thoughts-207-,,0,0,0,,Eu juro que um dia\Nvou retalhar aqueles caras!{OG}{I am so going to kill him someday! - Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.69,0:12:35.11,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Eu vou trazer aquela garota de volta!{I'll bring the girl back! - OG}{arch}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.57,0:12:39.70,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Você só está feliz porque ela\Nnão está no Arlong Park...{You're in high spirits, now that\Nyou know she's not in Arlong Park... - OG}{Now that you know she's not\Nin Arlong Park, you sure are chipper. - WF}{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.11,0:12:42.03,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Leme a estibordo, todo!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.03,0:12:44.66,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Leva o barco até o {\i1}Going Merry{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.66,0:12:46.62,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Certo!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.00,0:12:48.41,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Beleza!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.41,0:12:52.00,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Eu batizo este momento corajoso,\Nem que piso em solo desconhecido,{I hereby title this brave image of me about to tread unknown soil, - OG}{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.00,0:12:55.13,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,"A Grande Aventura do Capitão Usopp"!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.97,0:13:06.31,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Vocês estão bem?!{\fscx80\fscy80\bord3.04\shad3.04}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.31,0:13:07.47,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Ali! Ali!{\fscx80\fscy80\bord3.04\shad3.04}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.47,0:13:09.23,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Homens-peixe!{\pos(373,1053)}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.47,0:13:09.23,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Homens-peixe!{\pos(1062,1053)}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.98,0:13:11.52,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Toda velocidade à frente!{\fscx80\fscy80\bord3.04\shad3.04}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.52,0:13:12.94,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Sim, senhor!{\fscx80\fscy80\bord3.04\shad3.04}{Right! - OG}{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.19,0:13:17.19,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Por que você passou direto?!{OG}{Why did you just pass by them?! - Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.90,0:13:21.91,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Você viu aquilo?!\NTinham homens-peixe ali!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.91,0:13:25.08,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,É a tripulação do Arlong! Eles são assustadores!\NAlgum problema com isso?!{They're Arlong's crew! They're scary!\NSomethin' wrong with that?! - OG}{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.08,0:13:26.74,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Não grita comigo!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.16,0:13:31.21,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{I guess this whole area is\Nseriously under Arlong's control! - OG}{I guess this whole area is\Nreally under Arlong's control! - Gaijin}Parece que essa área toda\Nrealmente {\i1}está{\i0} sob o controle do Arlong!{WF+PP}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.71,0:13:32.67,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,E agora?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.75,0:13:36.46,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Beleza! É só dizer que\Nnão conseguimos trazer a Nami!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.46,0:13:39.92,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Me desamarrem, seus idiotas!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.67,0:13:42.22,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Nunca vi aquele barco antes...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.22,0:13:43.34,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Suspeito...{It's suspicious. - OG}{arch - alt: "That's suspicious."}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.26,0:13:46.93,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Hora de ir!{Escape! - OG}{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.93,0:13:47.64,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Concordo!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.64,0:13:50.06,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Esperem aí, seus dois!{Hold it, you two! - OG}{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.10,0:13:54.31,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,– Tchau!\N– Tchau!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.81,0:13:57.27,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Ei! Pelo menos me desamarrem!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.41,0:14:05.16,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Espera, o quê? Só um cara?{Huh? It's just him? - OG}{Wait, what? It's just him? - arch}{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.16,0:14:08.29,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Você é algum tipo\Nde náufrago ou algo assim?{Were you banished from\Nsomewhere or somethin'? - OG}{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.29,0:14:10.00,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,A-Acho que sim...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.00,0:14:11.96,Thoughts-207-,,0,0,0,,Eu vou matar aqueles caras!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.96,0:14:14.79,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Ah! Então você ficou assim\Npor ter sido torturado!{Ah! So you got these injuries\Nfrom being tortured! - OG}{GD}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.79,0:14:18.25,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Certo, vamos levá-lo\Npro Capitão Arlong!{Alright! Let's take him back\Nto Arlong-san for now! - OG}{PP}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.75,0:14:19.88,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Nos perdoe, Zoro!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.88,0:14:22.84,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Vou dizer pro Luffy que você morreu com honra!{I'll tell Luffy you were a truly brave man! - OG}{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.84,0:14:24.84,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Que azar!{What an unlucky person! - OG}{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.84,0:14:27.01,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Nunca vou te esquecer, Mano!{I'll never forget about you, Big Bro! - OG}{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.01,0:14:29.26,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Beleza, então! Vamos pra\Nterra firme por enquanto!{They sure got over that quick lol, WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.26,0:14:30.02,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Certo!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.19,0:14:38.27,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Deve ter uma cidade\Nchamada Gosa aqui perto!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.75,0:14:56.08,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,O-O que aconteceu aqui?!{Wh-What happened to this town?! - OG}{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.08,0:15:00.59,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Ouvi dizer que o Arlong destruiu\Ntudo algumas semanas atrás, mas...{I heard Arlong ravaged it\Na few weeks back, but... - OG}{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.59,0:15:04.55,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,A-As casas estão todas\Nde cabeça pra baixo!{A-All the houses have\Nbeen flipped over! - OG}{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.05,0:15:10.51,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Dizem que os homens-peixe são naturalmente\Ndez vezes mais fortes que humanos...!{I hear fishmen generally have\Nten times the strength of humans! - OG}{I hear fishmen are naturally\Nten times stronger than humans...! - Gaijin}{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.93,0:15:15.52,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,É disso que as pessoas\Nda Grand Line são capazes?{In short, could this be how strong\Npeople from the Grand Line are?! - OG}{Is this the caliber of people\Nfrom the Grand Line?! - Gaijin}{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.15,0:15:24.19,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Como a rua ficou desse jeito?{But how'd even the street get like this? - OG}{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.95,0:15:28.07,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Um monstro chamado Momoo fez isso.{That was the doing\Nof a monster called Momoo. - OG}{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.07,0:15:29.78,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Um monstro?{Monster? - OG}{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.78,0:15:33.08,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Eles têm monstros também?{This place even has monsters? - OG}{WF+PP}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.50,0:15:36.54,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Nós trouxemos ele lá\Nda Grand Line.{We brought him from the Grand Line. - OG}{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.33,0:15:39.17,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Da Grand Line, é?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.50,0:15:42.05,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{“We”? - OG}Espera, {\i1}nós{\i0}...?!{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.05,0:15:44.92,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Você tá com aquele náufrago, né?!{You're with that guy who\Ngot banished, aren't you?! - OG}{You're with that banished guy,\Naren't you?! - Gaijin}{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.47,0:15:49.85,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Tchau tchau!{Bye! - OG}{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.76,0:15:49.85,Secondary-207-,,0,0,0,,Volta aqui!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.30,0:15:52.47,Secondary-207-,,0,0,0,,De jeito nenhum!{\an8}{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.85,0:15:52.47,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Escapou por um triz...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.60,0:15:54.85,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Por favor, fique seguro...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.48,0:15:56.77,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Mano Usopp!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.77,0:15:59.77,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Vou esperar aqui pelo\NYosaku e pelo Mano Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.44,0:16:04.78,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Mesmo sendo um homem-peixe,\Nninguém me pega em terra firme!{As if a fishman can possibly\Ncatch me on dry land! - OG}{arch - alt: "You'll never catch me..."}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.19,0:16:07.28,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Estou acostumado com isso!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.28,0:16:10.03,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Me pega se conseguir!{Just try and catch up to me! - OG}{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.99,0:16:13.91,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Q-Que...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.91,0:16:15.87,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Te achei, homem-peixe!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.87,0:16:19.08,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Isso é pelo meu papai!\NEu vou te matar!{You killed my daddy!\NAnd I'm gonna kill you! - OG}{I'm gonna avenge my daddy! - Gaijin}{WF+PP}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.09,0:16:25.76,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Fique longe dos homens-peixe!{Don't mess with the fishmen! - OG}{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.76,0:16:28.88,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Não esqueça, todo mundo aqui em Gosa{Have you forgotten?! Everyone here in Gosa - OG}{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.88,0:16:33.06,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,foi massacrado porque\Num único morador os desafiou!{was slaughtered because just\None villager defied them! - OG}{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.22,0:16:36.27,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Espera aí...{Huh? - OG}{For real? - Gaijin}{PP - Literally "What" or "Huh"}{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.27,0:16:38.60,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Você parece um homem-peixe,\Nmas é humano.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.60,0:16:39.39,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Acho.{Just barely. - OG}{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.39,0:16:41.06,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Just barely?! - OG}Você {\i1}acha{\i0}?!{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.44,0:16:43.44,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Onde você está?! Ali?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.94,0:16:44.94,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Ele está vindo!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.94,0:16:46.44,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Um homem-peixe!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.44,0:16:47.95,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Tinha um de verdade também?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.53,0:16:51.78,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Pra trás!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.41,0:16:54.28,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Eu, Capitão Usopp, vou proteger vocês!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.28,0:16:56.25,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Devo conseguir lidar com um!{I can handle one easily enough! - OG}{I should be able\Nto handle a single one! - arch - lit: "If it's just one, I should be able to do something"}{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.00,0:16:59.04,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Toma essa!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.04,0:17:02.33,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Estrela de Chumbo Letal–{\fad(150,0)}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.84,0:17:10.88,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Ninguém nunca escuta!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.88,0:17:13.51,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Eu avisei, mexe com\Nos homens-peixe e estamos mortos!{I told you, the fishmen'll kill us if we mess with them! - OG}{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.44,0:17:26.32,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,O-Onde estou?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.32,0:17:27.69,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Na minha casa.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.36,0:17:30.70,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Acordou?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.70,0:17:31.86,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Q-Quem é você?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.28,0:17:34.03,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Sou a Nojiko.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.03,0:17:35.70,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Eu cultivo tangerinas aqui.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.70,0:17:38.70,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,É mesmo! Você me deu uma pancada!{That's right! You thwacked me! - OG}{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.25,0:17:42.50,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Justo quando eu estava tentando\Nte salvar, também!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.83,0:17:44.50,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Fui eu quem te salvou.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.84,0:17:47.96,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Se você tivesse feito qualquer coisa\Ncom aquele homem-peixe,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.96,0:17:50.55,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,com certeza estaria morto.{there's no question\Nyou would've been killed. - OG}{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.55,0:17:52.01,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Malditos forasteiros!{This is why I hate outsiders! - OG}{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.30,0:17:57.14,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Você, por outro lado,\Né de Gosa, né?{But you're a kid from Gosa, right? - OG}{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.10,0:18:00.52,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Você deveria saber\Npor experiência própria{Surely you know all too well from firsthand experience - OG}{CPS, WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.52,0:18:04.86,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,que vai morrer se\Nprovocar os homens-peixe.{that you'll be killed if you\Nmess with the fishmen. - OG}{WF+GD}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.86,0:18:06.61,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Eu sei disso...!{I know! - OG}{I know...! - Gaijin}{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.61,0:18:10.82,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Eu sei disso! Mas eles mataram meu papai!{I know, but... they killed my daddy! - OG}{I know, but they killed my daddy! - Gaijin}{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.36,0:18:14.11,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Eles roubaram tudo,\Ndestruíram nossa cidade,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.11,0:18:16.16,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,e mataram um monte de gente!{OG}{and slaughtered the villagers! - WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.16,0:18:17.58,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Eles têm que pagar!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.58,0:18:19.29,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Não importa o quê, eles têm que pagar!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.66,0:18:23.04,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Por isso eu fui ao Arlong Park!{So I went to Arlong Park! - OG}{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.04,0:18:26.29,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Mas uma mulher da\Ntripulação dele me impediu!{But a girl on his side got in the way! - OG}{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.42,0:18:30.63,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Ela...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.63,0:18:32.05,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,era como uma bruxa!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.84,0:18:34.38,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Eu odeio isso!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.38,0:18:37.01,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Não me importo se morrer;\Nvou vingar meu papai!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.01,0:18:38.26,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Então morra.{Cue tiktok, WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.81,0:18:42.77,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Se você está preparado pra morrer,\Nentão vá se vingar!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.77,0:18:44.73,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Mas lembre-se disso:{But know this much. - OG}{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.73,0:18:48.52,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Agora que a bruxa do Arlong Park\Ne eu te impedimos,{Now that me and that witch\Nat Arlong Park have stopped you, - OG}{PP}{GRAMMAR POLICE}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.94,0:18:51.44,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,você escapou da morte duas vezes!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.82,0:18:54.70,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Vá embora quando terminar o chá.{\q2}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.70,0:18:55.41,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Ei!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.41,0:18:58.37,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Não pode pegar leve com o garoto?!{Isn't that being\Na little harsh on the kid?! - OG}{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.37,0:19:01.91,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Garoto ou não, se alguém quer\Nmorrer, então deixa morrer!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.75,0:19:06.21,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Ele não tem coragem de viver\Npassando por dificuldades mesmo!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.21,0:19:07.33,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,O que quer dizer?{Say what? - OG}{What are you saying? - PP}{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.33,0:19:10.88,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Eu conheço uma garota que\Nestá focada no futuro,{I know a kid who's staring\Nfixedly at the distant future - OG}{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.88,0:19:13.84,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,enquanto suporta uma vida\Nmais dolorosa que a morte.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.59,0:19:19.97,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Por isso eu odeio gente como ele\Nque joga a vida fora!{That's why I hate people like him\Nwho consider death right off the bat! - OG}{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.47,0:19:26.10,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,O que... O que eu devo fazer, então?{What... should I do? - OG}{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.69,0:19:29.31,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Estou com tanta raiva! Mas vou aguentar!{I hate this! I'll endure it! - OG}{WF}{PP's TL - this is meant to be sth like "I'll endure my frustration"}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.19,0:19:31.27,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,E a sua mãe?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.65,0:19:35.28,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Ela está viva...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.20,0:19:39.20,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Ela deve estar morrendo de preocupação.{She's worried about you. - OG}{WF/PJ}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.20,0:19:40.53,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Volte pra ela.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.30,0:19:55.09,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Apesar das tatuagens,\Nvocê é bem legal!{You're actually a nice person!\NEven though you have tattoos... - OG}{Your tattoos are scary,\Nbut you're not half bad! - CPS, WF}{PJ/Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.09,0:19:56.26,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Que preconceito!{Prejudice! - OG}{That's discrimination! - WF}{TATTOO-IST! - WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.63,0:19:59.22,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Eu não sei nada\Nsobre você, sabia.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.22,0:20:00.76,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Ah, é mesmo!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.10,0:20:03.39,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Meu nome é Capitão Usopp!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.39,0:20:05.52,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Estou procurando uma garota chamada Nami...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.31,0:20:11.52,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,O quê?! A Nami é uma oficial\Ndos Piratas do Arlong?!{What?! Nami's a leader\Nof the Arlong Pirates?! - OG}{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.94,0:20:12.98,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Isso.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.98,0:20:15.15,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Todo mundo aqui sabe dela.{She's infamous in this area. - OG}{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.15,0:20:19.36,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Ela é a "bruxa"\Nque aquele garoto mencionou.{Even that little boy said\Nshe seemed like a witch. - OG}{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.36,0:20:23.20,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Engraçado, essa bruxa\Ncresceu nesta mesma casa.{Even more surprising,\Nthat witch grew up in this very house! - OG}{WF+PJ}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.71,0:20:30.04,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Eu e a Nami somos irmãs adotivas.{Me and Nami are adopted sisters. - OG}{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.54,0:20:34.21,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Então esta é...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.55,0:20:37.13,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,a casa da Nami?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.13,0:20:39.76,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Eu e a Nami somos órfãs.{Me and Nami are both orphans. - OG}{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.30,0:20:42.68,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Fomos criadas nesta casa.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.68,0:20:45.06,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Nossa mãe adotiva morreu,{Our foster parent is dead too, - OG}{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.06,0:20:49.27,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,mas nós três costumávamos viver\Nfelizes aqui na Vila Cocoyashi.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.02,0:20:56.40,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Então, a Nami traiu\Na própria mãe e a vila{Then... Nami betrayed her own\Nparent and fellow villagers - OG}{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.40,0:20:59.15,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,e se juntou à tripulação do Arlong?!{and joined Arlong's group?! - OG}{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.49,0:21:00.91,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,É, basicamente isso.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.91,0:21:02.95,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Uma verdadeira bruxa, hein?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.78,0:21:06.08,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Droga! Então era isso?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.08,0:21:08.71,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Ela nos enganou o tempo todo!{So she had us fooled the entire time! - OG}{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.71,0:21:11.63,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Ela estava atrás de tesouro\Ndesde o começo!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.63,0:21:14.84,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Mesmo depois de ter ajudado a lutar\Npra proteger a minha vila
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.84,0:21:18.34,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,e parecia tão feliz navegando com a gente!{and smiled so happily aboard our ship! - OG}{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.97,0:21:21.30,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Opa? Ela parecia feliz?{Oh? Happily? - OG}{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.09,0:21:24.30,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Ela?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.81,0:21:28.14,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Viemos aqui pra\Nlevá-la de volta com a gente,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.14,0:21:30.31,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,mas acho que não tem necessidade de–
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.77,0:21:40.49,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Isso me lembra, um amigo nosso\Ninfelizmente foi capturado pelos homens-peixe.{That reminds me, a friend of ours was unlucky enough to be caught by the fishmen... - OG}{\q2}{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.53,0:21:43.41,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Isso é ruim...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.41,0:21:45.74,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Será que ele está bem...{I wonder how the guy's holding up... - OG}{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.74,0:21:48.08,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Abram o portão!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.08,0:21:50.54,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Trouxemos alguém suspeito!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.09,0:22:02.84,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Vou perguntar de novo.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.84,0:22:05.85,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Por que exatamente você veio aqui?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.76,0:22:11.10,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Já disse — estou procurando\Numa garota, seu aberração meio-peixe!{I told you already—I'm looking\Nfor a girl! Half-fish bastard! - OG}{I told you already, I'm looking\Nfor a girl! Half-fish freak! - Gaijin}{Godamn Zoro, not cool. - WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.60,0:22:15.61,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Você fala demais\Npra um mero humano.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.61,0:22:19.07,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Vou te perdoar dessa vez,\Nmas nunca mais diga "meio-peixe".
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.07,0:22:23.03,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Nós homens-peixe somos humanos evoluídos\Nque ganharam a habilidade{We fishmen are "evolved humans"\Nwho've gained the ability - OG}{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.03,0:22:25.03,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,de respirar debaixo d'água.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.03,0:22:29.74,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Nossas qualidades aquáticas\Nnos tornam superiores a vocês.{Those fish abilities result\Nin us being superior to you. - OG}{Those fish abilities make\Nus superior to you. - Gaijin}{Lorphex}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.74,0:22:34.21,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Essas características são a prova\Nde que evoluímos muito além de vocês!{As proof, we possess numerous\Nabilities that surpass those of humans! - OG}{PP+WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.08,0:22:39.59,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Enfie na sua cabeça que\Nos homens-peixe são os senhores de tudo!{Get it through your head that\Nfishmen are the lord of all things! - OG}{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.59,0:22:44.18,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Humanos desafiando homens-peixe é basicamente\Ndesafiar as leis da natureza!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.84,0:22:48.31,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Estou farta do seu\Ndiscurso ridículo, Arlong.{I'm sick of those ridiculous\Nopinions of yours, Arlong. - OG}{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.52,0:22:52.93,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Não fique assim, Nami.{Don't look so stern, Nami. - OG}{Why'd ya gotta be so serious, Nami. - Gaijin}{Don't take it personally, Nami. - WF}{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.93,0:22:55.56,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Você pode ser humana,\Nmas é uma exceção.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.56,0:22:59.36,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Você é uma cartógrafa habilidosa e uma\Nmembra valiosa dos Piratas do Arlong!{You're a skilled surveyor and prized\Nmember of the Arlong Pirates! - OG}{You're a skilled surveyor and a prized\Nmember of the Arlong Pirates! - Gaijin}{PJ}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.36,0:23:02.15,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Suas cartas náuticas são incomparáveis!{You make truly accurate\Nsea charts for us! - OG}{You truly make the most\Naccurate sea charts! - Z}{PJ}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.57,0:23:05.78,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Eu sou muito mais esperta que vocês, idiotas.{I have far more smarts than you guys. - OG}{I'm much more intelligent\Nthan you guys. - Gaijin}{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.78,0:23:06.99,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,É natural.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.37,0:23:08.24,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Ei, Nami!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.24,0:23:09.95,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{What does he mean, “surveyor”?! - OG}What does he mean, “cartographer”?!{PJ}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.95,0:23:13.16,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Por que você está agindo toda\Nde amiguinha com esse cara?!{Why are you acting all\Nfriendly-like with this guy?! - OG}{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.16,0:23:15.96,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Oh? Ele é um conhecido seu?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.96,0:23:17.46,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Não seja ridículo!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.46,0:23:18.96,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Ele era mais uma vítima.{He was just my prey. - OG}{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.96,0:23:22.92,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Eu acabei de roubar um monte\Nde tesouro desse cara.{I swiped a whole load of treasure\Nfrom this guy this time around. - OG}{Gaijin}{I just relieved this guy\Nof all his treasure. - WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.42,0:23:27.43,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Não acredito que ele me seguiu até aqui\Nsem a menor ideia de que foi enganado.{To think he'd follow me here,\Nwithout any idea he'd been tricked... - OG}{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.43,0:23:28.89,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Que ingênuo.{Talk about unbelievably stupid. - OG}{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.51,0:23:31.89,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Então essas são suas verdadeiras cores, hein?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.89,0:23:34.39,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Depois de toda aquela conversa sobre odiar piratas.{After you hated pirates so much before. - OG}{After you talked so much\Nabout hating pirates. - Gaijin}{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.39,0:23:35.89,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Surpreso?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.89,0:23:37.90,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Foi tudo uma farsa.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.90,0:23:39.52,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Isso esclarece as coisas?{Does this make it clear enough? - OG}{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.15,0:23:43.65,Thoughts-207-,,0,0,0,,I-Isso é...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.20,0:23:54.04,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Eu sou uma pirata, simples assim!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.04,0:23:56.08,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Uma oficial dos Piratas do Arlong!{And a leader of the Arlong Pirates! - OG}{I'm an officer of the Arlong Pirates! - Gaijin}{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.67,0:24:00.92,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Cara, ela te enganou direitinho!{So you had them completely fooled! - OG}{So she fooled you completely! - arch: he's talking to Zoro}{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.67,0:24:03.92,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Essa garota é uma bruxa de sangue frio;{This girl's like a cold-blooded witch— - OG}{This girl's like a cold-blooded witch; - Gaijin}{PJ}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.92,0:24:08.13,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,ela ignora até a morte\Nda própria mãe por dinheiro!{she'll even forget about her\Nown parent's death for money! - OG}{she'll even overlook her own\Nparent's death for money! - Gaijin}{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.34,0:24:10.10,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Bem...{Gab}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.60,0:24:14.02,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,simplesmente aceite que foi azar\Nter cruzado com ela e desista.{Just chalk it up to bad luck\Nthat you crossed her and give up. - OG}{Gab}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.02,0:24:15.77,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Entendo.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.64,0:24:21.23,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Mas não é como se eu tivesse\Nconfiado nela desde o início.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.56,0:24:25.19,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Mesmo se ela fosse uma assassina em massa,\Neu não ficaria muito surpreso.{Even if she were a homicidal maniac,\NI wouldn't be too surprised. - OG}{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.19,0:24:28.70,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Nesse caso, dá pra sumir daqui?!\NEstou farta de olhar pra você!{In that case, could you get the hell\Nout of here?! You're an eyesore! - OG}{In that case, could you just go away?! You're an eyesore! - Gaijin}{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.58,0:24:43.84,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,O que aconteceu?! Por que ele\Npulou na água de repente?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.84,0:24:46.30,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Isso é algum tipo de truque?!{Is someone pulling\Nsome kinda lame joke? - OG}{Is this some kind of prank?! - Gaijin}{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.72,0:24:49.72,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Não, não é como se ele tivesse escorregado...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.72,0:24:51.01,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Então ele fugiu!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.43,0:24:55.97,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Não, os braços e pernas dele estão amarrados!\NEle não pode nadar assim!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.97,0:24:57.06,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,É suicídio.{It's a suicide! - OG}{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.73,0:24:58.94,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Deixem ele.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.52,0:25:04.07,Thoughts-207-,,0,0,0,,Aquele idiota!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.75,0:25:17.62,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Ele voltou.{He's back up! - OG}{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.62,0:25:20.29,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Ei! O que está acontecendo, Nami?!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.71,0:25:23.96,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,O que você estava pensando?!{What do you think you're doing?! - OG}{CPS, WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.84,0:25:29.17,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{No, what do you think you're doing?! - OG}Não, o que {\i1}você{\i0} estava pensando?{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.18,0:25:35.68,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Você é só uma garotinha que\Nnão aguenta ver um cara morrer...{You're just a small fry who\Ncan't even watch one guy die... - OG}{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.68,0:25:37.14,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Para de tentar se fazer de durão!{Quit tryin' to act cool! - OG}{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.64,0:25:42.10,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Me salva mais rápido da próxima vez, idiota!\NAchei que ia me afogar!{Save me sooner next time,\Nyou idiot! I thought I was gonna die! - OG}{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.98,0:25:44.56,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Vai se ferrar!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.11,0:25:48.40,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Mexa comigo de novo e eu te mato!{Mess with me any more\Nand you will die! - OG}{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.19,0:25:50.40,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Será?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.74,0:25:53.53,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Você está coberto de bandagens.{That's a lot of bandages you have. - OG}{You're covered in quite a few bandages. - Gaijin}{CPS, WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.53,0:25:56.83,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Não tinha roupa limpa,\Nentão usei essas no lugar.{Didn't have a change of clothes,\Nso I used these instead. - OG}{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.63,0:26:07.09,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Ei, Nami.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.09,0:26:08.59,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,O que fazemos com ele?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.59,0:26:09.92,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Prendam ele!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:09.92,0:26:11.63,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Eu mesma cuido dele!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:11.63,0:26:14.39,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Capitão Arlong! Capitão Arlong!{Arlong-san! Arlong-san! - OG}{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:15.68,0:26:17.31,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,O que foi, irmão?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:17.68,0:26:18.47,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Me desculpe!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:18.47,0:26:24.98,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Aquele cara tinha um amigo\Nnarigudo com ele, mas escapou!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.98,0:26:27.15,Thoughts-207-,,0,0,0,,Que droga, Usopp?!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.15,0:26:29.32,Thoughts-207-,,0,0,0,,Você acabou sendo\Ndescoberto mesmo assim?!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.32,0:26:30.36,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Acho que...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:30.36,0:26:33.49,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,ele pode ter fugido pra\NVila Cocoyashi...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.16,0:26:35.74,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Vila Cocoyashi, é?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.37,0:26:37.74,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Perfeito.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.74,0:26:39.70,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Também tenho assuntos lá.{I have other business there, too. - OG}{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:45.96,0:26:48.04,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Ei! O Arlong está vindo!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:48.04,0:26:49.59,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,O quê?!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.59,0:26:51.30,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Pra quê?!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:51.30,0:26:53.59,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Acabamos de pagar nosso tributo!{We just paid our tribute money to him! - OG}{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.51,0:26:58.47,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Provavelmente é por causa das\Nminhas armas que eles encontraram.{It's probably about the weapons\Nof mine they found... - OG}{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:58.47,0:27:00.52,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Voltem para suas casas, todos.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.52,0:27:01.89,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Sr. Gen...!{Gen-san! - OG}{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:02.81,0:27:03.98,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Eles chegaram!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:12.40,0:27:14.53,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Então você é o desgraçado...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:14.53,0:27:17.70,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,que estava com armas.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:17.70,0:27:19.74,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Sim, está correto.{Yes. That's right... - OG}{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:19.74,0:27:24.75,Main-207-,,0,0,10,,Sempre gostei de colecionar armas.{\q2}{Because I've always\Nenjoyed looking at weapons. - OG}{I've always enjoyed looking at weapons. - Gaijin}{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:24.75,0:27:28.71,Main-207-,,0,0,10,,Coleções também são proibidas\Nsob o seu governo?{Are collections not allowed\Nunder your rule, either? - OG}{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:29.17,0:27:31.25,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Sim, não posso permitir isso.{No, I can't have that. - OG}{the "no" doesn't make sense in the OG either, he's confirming what Genzo asked, WF}{PP - TL confirmed}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:31.71,0:27:34.59,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Armas só geram\Npensamentos maldosos e violência.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:34.59,0:27:37.72,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,São a principal causa\Nde perturbação da paz.{They're the chief things\Nthat undermine peace. - OG}{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:39.05,0:27:41.68,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Ele é enorme! {\i1}Aquele{\i0} é o Arlong?!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:41.68,0:27:43.27,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,E-Ele não é humano!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:43.27,0:27:45.35,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Pois é. Porque ele é um homem-peixe.{Nope. Because he's a fishman. - OG}{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:45.35,0:27:46.23,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Ah, é mesmo.{Yeah... - OG}{Oh, yeah. - Gaijin}{Makes sense. - arch}{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:46.56,0:27:49.81,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Eu controlo vinte cidades e vilas.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:49.81,0:27:54.07,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Como seu supervisor,\Nnão posso tolerar rebeliões.{As their manager,\NI can't afford to have rebellions. - OG}{WF+GD}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:54.07,0:27:59.78,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Eu destruí a grande cidade portuária de Gosa\Ncomo exemplo para as outras comunidades!{\q2}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:59.78,0:28:01.99,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Não conseguir pagar o tributo{The blunder of being\Nunable to pay tribute money - OG}{The mistake of being unable\Nto pay tribute money - Gaijin}{CPS, WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:02.45,0:28:05.33,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,é um ato de rebelião contra nós!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:05.33,0:28:06.46,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Ei!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:06.46,0:28:07.83,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Pagar tributo?{Tribute money? - OG}{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:07.83,0:28:09.21,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Exatamente o que parece.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:09.21,0:28:11.29,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,É o dinheiro que oferecemos a eles.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:11.79,0:28:15.80,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Todo mês, compramos\Nnossas vidas com dinheiro.{We buy our lives every\Nmonth with money. - OG}{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:15.80,0:28:17.80,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Adultos e crianças...{Adults and kids... - OG}{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:17.80,0:28:20.80,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Se alguém da vila não conseguir\Npagar o tributo...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:20.80,0:28:22.89,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,mesmo que seja só uma pessoa...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:22.89,0:28:25.64,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,a vila será\Naniquilada como Gosa.{the village gets wiped out\Njust like Gosa Town. - OG}{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:25.64,0:28:29.23,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Então aquela cidade enorme foi destruída\Npor causa de uma pessoa só?!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:29.23,0:28:31.02,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,É assim que o Arlong governa.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:31.48,0:28:35.44,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Eles são obcecados por espécie e não\Nestão nem aí pra matar humanos.{They're species-obsessed and don't\Ngive a damn about killing people. - OG}{Gaijin/Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:35.44,0:28:36.82,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Prestem atenção.{Listen. - OG}{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:36.82,0:28:41.95,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Humanos insignificantes não devem se\Npreocupar com nada além de continuar pagando!{You lowly humans simply need\Nto keep paying up without thinking! - OG}{You lowly humans simply need\Nto mindlessly keep paying up! - Gaijin}{All you puny humans need to do\Nis keep paying up mindlessly! - WF}{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:42.70,0:28:46.08,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Eu preciso de enormes quantias de dinheiro!{I need enormous funds! - OG}{Gaijin}{You'll give me every Belly you have! - Lorphex}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:46.08,0:28:50.21,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,O dinheiro do tributo de vocês\Neventualmente se tornará a base
Dialogue: 0,0:28:50.21,0:28:53.42,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,do Império Arlong,\Nque governará o East Blue!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:55.00,0:28:57.30,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,I-Império Arlong?!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:58.80,0:29:03.47,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Eles planejam transformar todo o\NEast Blue num império de homens-peixe?!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:23.24,0:29:24.87,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Saia daqui.{Hurry and escape. - OG}{Just get out of here. - Gaijin}{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:24.87,0:29:26.87,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Antes que o Arlong volte.
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{=33}===============================DIALOGUE============================
